title: Larry Hernandez Freed: Reality Star Released On Bail In Kidnapping Case
text:
Published By: Hollywood Life - Today 
Mexican singer Larry Hernandez has been freed on a $200,000 bail after being extradited to South Carolina for kidnapping and assault charge...
